resolution: "Restored reproducible grouped updates, adopted checkout/setup-node v7 and action-gh-release v3, and constrained unsupported TypeScript/Node-typing major churn while preserving compatible updates."
expected_result: All maintained Action majors run successfully and Dependabot proposes only updates compatible with the supported toolchain/runtime contracts.
actual_result: "PR #55 and merged-head CI/Security/release verification passed; policy refresh succeeded; zero open PRs, issues, or security alerts remain."
dependencies[1]{id,kind,created_at,author,source_kind}:
