comments[9]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:54:19.097Z",codex-root,Representative GitHub Actions runs 26775340556 and 26673365486 fail before tests.
  "2026-07-16T17:08:03.440Z",codex-root,"Official actionlint 1.7.12 found SC2034 in publish.yml: a shell VERSION assignment was dead because the validator reads the step-level environment variable. Removed the dead assignment and preserved the validation contract."
  "2026-07-16T17:15:52.133Z",codex-root,"Hosted PR #52 exposed a CI-only commit-audit defect: actions/checkout checks out the synthetic merge ref without a local master branch, so the script's hard-coded master revision failed before inspecting any commits. Fixed the auditor to use origin/..HEAD for pull-request runs and HEAD for complete-history local/push runs; both modes pass locally."
  "2026-07-16T17:16:00.596Z",codex-root,"Correction to the preceding comment: the pull-request range is origin/${GITHUB_BASE_REF}..HEAD; shell interpolation in the command that recorded the earlier comment omitted the variable name from its rendered text."
  "2026-07-16T17:17:29.420Z",codex-root,The corrected hosted log then showed GitHub synthetic merge commit b8ac2ff as the sole non-conforming subject. Added git log --no-merges so generated merge commits are excluded while all authored commits in the base-to-head range remain audited.
  "2026-07-16T17:23:19.908Z",codex-root,"Exact PR head a481464 passed quality (bun), quality (node), coverage, package-smoke, commit-audit, history-scan, Dependency audit, PR title, and CodeQL before merge. Post-merge CI run 29519298326 and Security run 29519298269 both succeeded at d2c73b2; all stale Dependabot PRs are closed."
  "2026-07-16T17:25:16.027Z",codex-root,Reopened canonical CI/dependency automation item. PR #53 validly updates newly released checkout v7 setup-node v7 and action-gh-release v3 and is green; PR #54 proposes TypeScript 7 and Node 26 typings against the documented TypeScript-ESLint and Node 22 contracts and fails frozen install across all dependency-consuming jobs.
  "2026-07-16T17:26:24.570Z",codex-root,"Local follow-up validation passes: frozen install lint typecheck build zero-vulnerability audit official actionlint 1.7.12 and YAML parsing. Adopted checkout v7 setup-node v7 and action-gh-release v3 exactly as green PR #53; added major ignores that explain and prevent failing PR #54 churn."
  "2026-07-16T17:31:21.805Z",codex-root,"Follow-up PR #55 exact head 776e40c passed Bun/Node quality, coverage, package smoke, commit audit, dependency audit, history scan, PR title, CodeQL, and review-status gates; merged as 3aa63d2. Post-merge CI 29519944470 and Security 29519944417 succeeded. Dependabot policy refresh jobs succeeded; #53 is superseded, #54 closed under the compatible-major policy, and the open PR/issue/alert inventories are empty."
notes[3]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:54:19.097Z",codex-root,"The failure is infrastructure-wide,not specific to Vitest or Commander behavior."
  "2026-07-16T17:10:22.123Z",codex-root,Official actionlint 1.7.12 and YAML 2.9 parsing both pass after removing the dead VERSION assignment and using a folded YAML scalar.
  "2026-07-16T17:26:24.570Z",codex-root,"Dependabot major ignores are deliberately narrow: TypeScript stays below the typescript-eslint 8.64 peer ceiling and @types/node stays aligned with the supported Node 22 runtime; compatible minor and patch updates remain enabled."
learnings[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:54:19.097Z",codex-root,Inspect one representative failure before changing source; shared pre-test failures usually belong to the dependency workflow.
  "2026-07-16T17:26:24.570Z",codex-root,Immediately after grouping configuration lands Dependabot can regenerate previously closed updates against newer releases; shipping closeout must re-check the bot queue after the default branch changes.
