close_reason: "Latest Action majors and compatible Dependabot update policy are merged, green, and backlog-clean."
body: "## Reproduction\\n\\nOpen Dependabot PR 51 or 50. Every CI matrix job stops at bun install --frozen-lockfile with lockfile had changes. Runner also warns checkout/setup-node v4 use deprecated Node 20 action runtimes."
